Required format:
YYYY-MM-DDTHH:mm:ss-03:00

Examples:
- 2026-05-05T09:00:00-03:00
- 2026-12-21T14:30:00-03:00

Use only a datetime based on a slot returned by the availabilities tool.
Do not invent times.
